<section class="py-20 bg-black relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 w-96 h-96 bg-gray-900 rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-center mb-16 text-white">Our Story</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg transform rotate-3"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="carousel relative">
            <img 
              src="/images/couple-photo.jpg" 
              alt="Our Journey" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded carousel-image"
            />
            <img 
              src="/images/couple-photo-2.jpg" 
              alt="Our Journey" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded carousel-image"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert">
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">We were just 20 when we got married. By 24, we had five beautiful children. It's been a journeyâ€”a whirlwind of growth, laughter, tears, and lessons we never saw coming.</p>
        
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">Our love has never been better, but it didn't happen overnight. We've spent years working, failing, learning, and trying again.</p>
        
        <p class="mb-6 text-gray-300">If you're married, engaged, or just dating, we invite you to join us on this journey. Let's grow together.</p>

        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/episodes" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors duration-200 no-underline"
          >
            Episodes
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .carousel {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .carousel-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .carousel-image:first-child {
    position: relative;
  }

  @keyframes carousel {
    0%, 40% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    50%, 90% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .carousel-image {
    animation: carousel 7s infinite;
  }

  .carousel-image:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 3.5s;
  }
</style>